Ext.data.JsonP['Appcelerator_CLI_5.1.0_Release_Note']({"guide":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\" ?>\n<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\"\n        \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\n<head>\n    <title>Appcelerator CLI 5.1.0 - 20 November 2015</title>\n\n    <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n    <meta content=\"Scroll EclipseHelp Exporter\" name=\"generator\">\n\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" media=\"print\">\n</link></link></link></meta></meta></head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"header\"/>\n\n        <div id=\"src-46239625\" class=\"content\">\n                        <h1>Appcelerator CLI 5.1.0 - 20 November 2015</h1>\n    <p>Appcelerator CLI 5.1.0 is a minor release that includes improvements and bug fixes.    </p>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-46239625_AppceleratorCLI5.1.0ReleaseNote-ComponentVersions\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Component Versions</span></h2>\n    <p>The following components are shipped with CLI 5.1.0:    </p>\n    <div class=\"tablewrap\">\n        <table class=\"confluenceTable\">\n        <thead class=\" \">    <tr>\n            <td class=\"confluenceTh\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>Name    </p>\n            </td>\n                <td class=\"confluenceTh\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>Version    </p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n</thead><tfoot class=\" \"/><tbody class=\" \">    <tr>\n            <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>Alloy    </p>\n            </td>\n                <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>1.7.26    </p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n    <tr>\n            <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p><strong class=\" \"><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/API_Builder_Release_Notes\">Arrow Builder</a></strong>    </p>\n            </td>\n                <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p><strong class=\" \">1.3.22</strong>    </p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n    <tr>\n            <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>Arrow Cloud CLI    </p>\n            </td>\n                <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>1.0.31    </p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n    <tr>\n            <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>Titanium CLI    </p>\n            </td>\n                <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>5.0.5    </p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n</tbody>        </table>\n            </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-46239625_AppceleratorCLI5.1.0ReleaseNote-FixedIssuesandImprovements\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Fixed Issues and Improvements</span></h2>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\"p1 \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/CLI-615\" target=\"_blank\">CLI-615</a>: Unable to run &apos;appc setup&apos; on io.js    </p>\n</li><li class=\"p1 \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/CLI-616\" target=\"_blank\">CLI-616</a>: Building to android with SDK 3.5.1.GA fails when using appc cli 0.2.280    </p>\n</li><li class=\"p1 \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/CLI-691\" target=\"_blank\">CLI-691</a>: Using invalid connector on appc install returns error    </p>\n</li><li class=\"p1 \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/CLI-728\" target=\"_blank\">CLI-728</a>: Appc info should not require login    </p>\n</li><li class=\"p1 \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/CLI-740\" target=\"_blank\">CLI-740</a>: Remove unnecessary secondary call to retrieve user information    </p>\n</li><li class=\"p1 \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/CLI-817\" target=\"_blank\">CLI-817</a>: Update alloy hook file in the project before invoking alloy build    </p>\n</li><li class=\"p1 \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/CLI-825\" target=\"_blank\">CLI-825</a>: Publishing a stable version of appc-cli doesn&apos;t tag it as latest    </p>\n</li><li class=\"p1 \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/CLI-828\" target=\"_blank\">CLI-828</a>: Add &quot;bugs&quot; URL to package.json    </p>\n</li><li class=\"p1 \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/CLI-832\" target=\"_blank\">CLI-832</a>: Add additional logging for Arrow cloud login calls    </p>\n</li><li class=\"p1 \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/CLI-838\" target=\"_blank\">CLI-838</a>: Cannot login to prod; body parameters error    </p>\n</li><li class=\"p1 \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/CLI-856\" target=\"_blank\">CLI-856</a>: In Appc CLI, if you create a project with European character sets, then the CLI prompt will not accept them    </p>\n</li><li class=\"p1 \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/CLI-865\" target=\"_blank\">CLI-865</a>: If incorrect credentials are input on login then the CLI will error with &apos;The registry server is currently unavailable&apos;    </p>\n</li><li class=\"p1 \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/CLI-869\" target=\"_blank\">CLI-869</a>: In preprod, you cannot import a mobile project with a non-platform guide    </p>\n</li></ul>    </div>\n        </div><a id=\"editButton\" href=\"https://wiki.appcelerator.org/pages/editpage.action?pageId=46239625\"><span>Edit</span></a>\n    \n        \n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","title":"Appcelerator CLI 5.1.0 Release Note"});